* Mishima Shrine
* Suwa Shrine
* Yasaka Shrines – 2
* Taga Shrine
* Sugawara Shrine
* Kotohira Shrine
* Agatsuma Shrines – 2
* Afuri Shrine
* Ontake Shrine

